Magmatron is in a secret room.

::Magmatron::

    He sent a hologram of himself to Like-Like's position in the 
Sulaco. "So, you have come to talk to me?"
    Magmatron (real one) turned to Cygnar. "We have a visitor, I will 
commense your training soon, but now I have to go and talk."
    He left the room, and took the place of the hologram.
